00</guid></item><item><title>无人机的黄金：大规模泄漏揭示了俄罗斯的伊朗沙赫德项目</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/gold-for-drones-massive-leak-reveals-the-iranian-shahed-project-in-russia/0000018d-bb85-dd5e-a59d-ffb729890000</link><description>文件揭示了售价 20 万美元的 Shahed 136 如何成为俄罗斯在乌克兰武库中的致命武器，以及先进型号的外观</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:51:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/gold-for-drones-massive-leak-reveals-the-iranian-shahed-project-in-russia/0000018d-bb85-dd5e-a59d-ffb729890000</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦真的“代表巴勒斯坦”吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/does-pakistan-really-stand-for-palestine/0000018d-cb11-d09f-a3df-ebb500570000</link><description>从文学节到政治神职人员，加沙战争加剧了巴基斯坦对以色列本已过度的敌意。虽然崇尚美德的进步人士和反犹太主义伊斯兰主义者在庆祝哈马斯方面找到了共同点，但他们真正在做什么来拯救巴勒斯坦人的生命呢？</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:42:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/does-pakistan-really-stand-for-palestine/0000018d-cb11-d09f-a3df-ebb500570000</guid></item><item><title>巴西总统用几句话抹去了他与以色列和犹太复国主义的所有热情联系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/in-a-few-sentences-brazils-president-erased-all-his-warm-connections-with-israel/0000018d-caab-d7bf-a19d-eebf5c530000</link><description>作为以色列的长期朋友和支持者，卢拉总统将以色列在加沙的行动与纳粹针对犹太人的行动进行了比较，这让总统与以色列之间数十年的善意化为泡影。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:36:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/in-a-few-sentences-brazils-president-erased-all-his-warm-connections-with-israel/0000018d-caab-d7bf-a19d-eebf5c530000</guid></item><item><title>叙利亚称以色列空袭大马士革居民区，造成两人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/syria-says-israeli-strikes-hit-damascus-residential-area-killing-two/0000018d-caf0-d09f-a3df-eaf498230000</link><description>以色列尚未证实袭击事件，但叙利亚人权组织负责人表示，袭击事件与上个月在贝鲁特发生的哈马斯高级官员被暗杀事件类似</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:03:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/syria-says-israeli-strikes-hit-damascus-residential-area-killing-two/0000018d-caf0-d09f-a3df-eaf498230000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷第二圣殿的奇怪石盒被发现。这是犹太洁食吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-21/ty-article/strange-stone-box-from-second-temple-jerusalem-is-revealed-was-it-kosher/0000018d-cad5-ddae-a18f-ffff2aa30000</link><description>这个盒子由石灰石制成，就像古代犹太家庭典型的石质厨具一样，盒子上有炭化痕迹——这是 2000 年前耶路撒冷被罗马人摧毁的痕迹</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 09:09:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-21/ty-article/strange-stone-box-from-second-temple-jerusalem-is-revealed-was-it-kosher/0000018d-cad5-ddae-a18f-ffff2aa30000</guid></item><item><title>对于内塔尼亚胡来说，停滞是完美的环境。对于以色列来说，这意味着灾难</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/for-netanyahu-stagnation-is-the-perfect-environment-for-israel-it-spells-disaster/0000018d-c88b-ddae-a18f-ffbf6c030000</link><description>尽管上周反对党因政府试图将卡西夫逐出议会而陷入内讧，但联盟成员的信心却在不断增强。尽管艾森科特比甘茨更激进，但他们都陷入了同一个陷阱</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 04:06:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/for-netanyahu-stagnation-is-the-perfect-environment-for-israel-it-spells-disaster/0000018d-c88b-ddae-a18f-ffbf6c030000</guid></item><item><title>在美国加大努力斡旋人质释放协议后，以色列持谨慎乐观态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-cautiously-optimistic-after-u-s-ramps-up-efforts-to-broker-a-hostage-release-deal/0000018d-c82a-ddae-a18f-ffbea2f30000</link><description>几周以来，耶路撒冷首次出现了一些乐观情绪，认为美国谈判另一项协议的努力将取得成果。会谈目前集中在几个关键问题上，主要是以色列将释放的人质与巴勒斯坦囚犯的比例以及停火将持续多久</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 04:02:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-cautiously-optimistic-after-u-s-ramps-up-efforts-to-broker-a-hostage-release-deal/0000018d-c82a-ddae-a18f-ffbea2f30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军律师称，一些士兵在加沙从事犯罪行为；叙利亚报道以色列袭击大马士革</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article-live/qatar-says-medicine-delivered-to-hostages-u-s-vetoes-un-resolution-demanding-cease-fire/0000018d-c9ac-d09f-a3df-e9bcee6d0000</link><description>叙利亚报告以色列袭击大马士革居民区 ■ 伊朗指责以色列破坏天然气管道 ■ 据报道以色列袭击加沙车辆造成人员伤亡 ■ 以色列国防军士兵在加沙战斗中丧生 ■ 美国否决了安理会要求立即停火的决议；提出呼吁“临时停火”的决议草案</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 03:36:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article-live/qatar-says-medicine-delivered-to-hostages-u-s-vetoes-un-resolution-demanding-cease-fire/0000018d-c9ac-d09f-a3df-e9bcee6d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长警告内塔尼亚胡政府：不要使用执法手段镇压抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-warns-netanyahus-government-dont-use-law-enforcement-to-quash-protests/0000018d-c896-d09f-a3df-e8b6c4e70000</link><description>加利·巴哈拉夫-米亚拉要求高等法院驳回内盖夫发展部长对她和州检察官提起的诉讼，试图迫使他们起诉反司法改革抗议者</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 22:25:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-warns-netanyahus-government-dont-use-law-enforcement-to-quash-protests/0000018d-c896-d09f-a3df-e8b6c4e70000</guid></item><item><title>亲以色列的福音派资金帮助特朗普最新的总统竞选提供资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-pro-israel-evangelical-money-helping-bankroll-trumps-latest-presidential-run/0000018d-c673-d207-a9dd-ff7b61290000</link><description>德克萨斯州福音派石油公司高管蒂姆·邓恩是唐纳德·特朗普竞选活动近期最引人注目的捐助者之一。与他一起的还有一些熟悉的亲以色列犹太商人，他们没有被特朗普对共和党的孤立主义压制吓倒</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 20:30:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-pro-israel-evangelical-money-helping-bankroll-trumps-latest-presidential-run/0000018d-c673-d207-a9dd-ff7b61290000</guid></item><item><title>以色列财政部长称遣返加沙人质“不是最重要的事情”，引发愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-20/ty-article/.premium/finance-minister-sparks-outrage-after-saying-returning-hostages-not-most-important-thing/0000018d-c7f2-d00f-a1df-dff6849c0000</link><description>在特拉维夫国防部门前的言论之后的一场自发示威中，一名被囚禁的 18 岁青少年的父亲对斯莫特里奇说道：“如果有人认为人质不重要，那就让他们绑架你的孩子吧。”孩子们，然后你们就可以说话了”</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 19:29:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-20/ty-article/.premium/finance-minister-sparks-outrage-after-saying-returning-hostages-not-most-important-thing/0000018d-c7f2-d00f-a1df-dff6849c0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么伯尼·桑德斯和 AOC 不会指责以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-20/ty-article/.highlight/why-bernie-sanders-aoc-wont-accuse-israel-of-genocide-in-gaza/0000018d-c762-d00f-a1df-df76f57b0000</link><description>进步左翼最具标志性的两位火炬手——参议员伯尼·桑德斯和众议员亚历山大·奥卡西奥-科尔特斯——故意不与他们的同事和大部分支持者的言论相匹配</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 18:54:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-20/ty-article/.highlight/why-bernie-sanders-aoc-wont-accuse-israel-of-genocide-in-gaza/0000018d-c762-d00f-a1df-df76f57b0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯高级成员表示政治领袖的开罗之行并不表明谈判取得突破</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-02-20/ty-article/.premium/senior-hamas-member-says-political-chiefs-trip-to-cairo-doesnt-indicate-breakthrough/0000018d-c7ac-d00f-a1df-dfbe798b0000</link><description>以色列人质家属抗议，要求政府派遣自己的代表前往埃及参加停火谈判，消息人士称以色列和哈马斯正试图在下个月内敲定一项协议</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 18:36:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-02-20/ty-article/.premium/senior-hamas-member-says-political-chiefs-trip-to-cairo-doesnt-indicate-breakthrough/0000018d-c7ac-d00f-a1